lenders.name: Roberto
lenders.loan_because:
I believe in a world of global citizens that understand the complexities of daily life - or at least attempt to understand the general notion.  A world in which individuals that have some capacity to assist others,   are willing to make change, and become a part of a larger support network; a network that is proactively influencing the world to make society a better place to live.  The Kiva Network is a group of people that support the principle of community.  Providing even a small loan can help foster a strong sense of empowerment,  confidence, respect, and 'belonging' for entrepreneurs.  I choose to loan because I choose to make a difference in the life of another human being.  I am a strong believer in reciprocal altruism, and I have faith as well as hope, directed towards a better, stronger, world.  

"The world is very different now. For man holds in his mortal hands the power to abolish all forms of human poverty and all forms of human life" -John F. Kennedy
